{"id": 1565, "title": "Ticket #1565: condor_ssh_to_job fails when SHELL=csh", "description": "<blockquote>\nSome versions of ssh invoke the <code>ProxyCommand</code> by using the shell specified via the SHELL environment variable (or /bin/sh if unset).  If csh is used, all file descriptors other than the stdio streams are closed.  This prematurely closes the socket that we are trying to pass down to the proxy command.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2010-Aug-06 09:52</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=25617\">[25617]</a></span>: Documented fix for condor_ssh_to_job and SHELL=csh. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=1565\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1565'); return false;\" title=\"condor_ssh_to_job fails when SHELL=csh\">#1565</a></span>  (By Dan Bradley )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2010-Aug-06 09:30</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=18738\">[18738]</a></span>: Fixed problem in condor_ssh_to_job when the user's shell is csh. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=1565\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1565'); return false;\" title=\"condor_ssh_to_job fails when SHELL=csh\">#1565</a></span>  (By Dan Bradley )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2010-Aug-06 10:01", "status": "resolved", "created": "2010-Aug-06 09:28", "fixed_version": "2010-Aug-06 09:28", "broken_version": "v070302", "priority": "4", "subsystem": "",